 y←s×⌊ymd÷10000 ⋄ m←100|⌊ymd÷100 ⋄ ym←(m-1)+12×y-1 ⍝ Relative month #
 ym←ym-(100|ymd)<start ⍝ Wrap to previous month if before start day
 m←1+12|ym ⋄ s←¯1*0>y←1+⌊ym÷12
 begin←(start-1)+JD s×(10000×|y)+(100×m)+1
